article_title: Down-ticket statewide candidates at Fancy Farm reference manure and pedicures
article_text: FANCY FARM — Pedicures were a topic for the candidates for attorney general, and a candidate for agriculture commissioner contended that his experience in shoveling manure on the family farm prepared him for state politics.
